      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Kieren Pearson</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"/File:KierenPearson.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/f/fc/KierenPearson.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:KierenPearson.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Kieren Pearson <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Kieren Pearson</b>,<br />\nan Australian bachelor of actuarial studies and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bachelor_of_Commerce\">bachelor of commerce</a> student at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_New_South_Wales\">UNSW</a>, self-employed mathematics tutor, and computer games and chess programmer.\nHe is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Halogen\" title=\"Halogen\">Halogen</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2019\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2019</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieren_Pearson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2019\">2019</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieren_Pearson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2019\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?t=11671\">Requirements for a new chess engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, December 09, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieren_Pearson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/discussion-board/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=12174\">Halogen 4 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">CCRL Discussion Board</a>, June 22, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=308\">Re: New engine releases 2020</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 12, 2020 &#160;» <a href=\"/Halogen\" title=\"Halogen\">Halogen</a> 6</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=74955&amp;start=2\">Re: Train a neural network evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75088&amp;start=2\">Re: SMP, first shot at implementation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 12, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=390\">Re: New engine releases 2020</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 22, 2020 &#160;» <a href=\"/Halogen\" title=\"Halogen\">Halogen</a> 7</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75190&amp;start=4\">Re: First success with neural nets</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 24, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=75195\">Test position for weak (~2500) engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 24, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=457\">Re: New engine releases 2020</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Kieren Pearson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 27, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Halogen\" title=\"Halogen\">Halogen</a> 8</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieren_Pearson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/KierenP\">KierenP (Kieren Pearson) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/KierenP/Halogen\">GitHub - KierenP/Halogen: A c++ chess engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/KierenP/ChessTrainingSets\">GitHub - KierenP/ChessTrainingSets: A collection of datasets for training chess engines</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/kieren-pearson-106988172/\">Kieren Pearson | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://math.stackexchange.com/users/297523/kieren-pearson\">User Kieren Pearson - Mathematics Stack Exchange</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/users/5030766/kieren-pearson\">User Kieren Pearson - Stack Overflow</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Kieren_Pearson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www